<br />Not very.  I kinda like the super sharp video on the VGA though... However it does output NTSC and s-video anyways so if you REALLY wanna use NTSC, there ya go <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":-)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br />Obviously, going from NTSC to RGB in the FPGA wouldn't be terribly practical, AFAIK... there's just too much processing that has to be done I think.  I can't 100% rule it out, but I don't think it is possible to do.</div>

					
